(0, 0, 0); text-align: justify; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: georgia, serif; line-height: 22px; background: transparent;">Please use this sub catagory to get better informed about PSC exam. We will do our best to ensure that information presented is accurate and up-to-date.</span></h2>\r\n<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: ''PT Sans Narrow'', sans-serif; line-height: 18px; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">\r\n	<div style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">\r\n		<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(126, 209, 217); outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(136, 28, 18); font-stretch: normal; font-family: Arial; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">\r\n			<a href="http://www.vetnepal.com/uploads/files/PSC_Syllabus.pdf" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(188, 45, 35); background: transparent;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background: transparent;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: georgia, serif; background: transparent;">1. Veterinary and Livestock GIII PSC Syllabus&nbsp;</span></span></span></a></p>\r\n		<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(126, 209, 217); outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(136, 28, 18); font-stretch: normal; font-family: Arial; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">\r\n			<a href="http://www.vetnepal.com/content.php?id=398" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(188, 45, 35); background: transparent;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background: transparent;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: georgia, serif; background: transparent;">2. Quick Review on Animal Breeding</span></span></span></a></p>\r\n		<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(126, 209, 217); outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(136, 28, 18); font-stretch: normal; font-family: Arial; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">\r\n			<span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: georgia, serif; background: transparent;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background: transparent;">3.</span><a href="http://www.vetnepal.com/content.php?id=402" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(188, 45, 35); background: transparent;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background: transparent;">Quick Review on Veterinary Planning and Extention</span></a></span></span></p>\r\n		<p style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border-width: 0px 0px 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(126, 209, 217); outline: 0px; font-size: 18px; vertical-align: baseline; text-align: justify; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(136, 28, 18); font-stretch: normal; font-family: Arial; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-color: transparent; background-size: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-position: initial; background-repeat: initial;">\r\n			<a href="http://www.vetnepal.com/content.php?id=403" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; text-decoration: none; color: rgb(188, 45, 35); background: transparent;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background: transparent;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; vertical-align: baseline; font-family: georgia, serif; background: transparent;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 14px; vertical-align: baseline; background: transparent;">4. Quick Review on Veterinary Parasitolog